HEADWORD: Bombastry
<hw>Bom"bast*ry</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Swelling words
without much meaning; bombastic language; fustian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Bombastry</qex> and buffoonery, by nature lofty and light,
soar highest of all.</q> <rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bombax</ent>⟦br⟧
